title: Apartment for Rent: Entrepotbrug 151
description: STUNNING VIEW! LOCATION: From this quiet part of Amsterdam (Amsterdam East/Zeeburg), you can reach the city center in no time. But you don't even have to go far for trendy places; Amsterdam East is hip & happening! For recreation, you can visit Oosterpark and Flevopark. LAYOUT: Take the elevator to the fourth floor, then the stairs to the third floor. Enter the apartment, which has a closed kitchen with a standard kitchenette and two bedrooms...
